    "# 🛢️ Step 3 - Data Preparation\n",
    "\n",
    "✍️ Data preparation transforms raw data into a suitable format for machine learning models, enhancing their accuracy and efficiency. Your task is to clean, transform, and organize the DoorDash data. Here are suggestions:\n",
    "\n",
    "*   Format Fields: Ensure data types are appropriate for analysis (e.g., datetime, categorical).\n",
    "*   Split Data: Divide the dataset into training and testing sets to evaluate model performance robustly.\n",
